                                                                                   "Ludger Jansen" ;
                                           <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> "Giorgio A. Ubbiali" ;     
                                           <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> """ClimOO Ontology is a reference ontology, modeling plastics, (micro-)plastic pollution, climate change, and their interrelation, with a primary focus on agricultural systems. The ClimOO Ontology is structured in a suite of nested ontological modules. The Plastics Interconnecting with Climate Change Ontology (PICCO) module extends PlasticO and ClimOO-SDC2 modules to represent impacts of and interrelations between (micro-)plastic pollution and climate change. A particular emphasis is dedicated such to phenomena with respect to soils. """@en ;
                                           <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> "https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/" ;
                                           <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "ClimOO Ontology - PICCO module"@en ;
                                           owl:versionInfo "2026-07-16"@en ,
                                                           "V1.0.0."@en ;
                                           <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#note> """Repository: https://www.w3id.org/climoo/repo
Documentation webpage: https://www.w3id.org/climoo/docs"""@en ,
                                                                                      "The most recent version of this file is available on GitHub at the following link: https://www.w3id.org/climoo/climoo-picco."@en .
               

